        <item>
            <title>【走塑】供應商示範竹刀叉鋸扒但兩度截斷，負責人：市民需時間適應</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/25/bamboo-knife-cut-steak-broke-twice/life-tech/green-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=bamboo-knife-cut-steak-broke-twice</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/25/bamboo-knife-cut-steak-broke-twice/life-tech/green-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 11:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[環保]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[即棄膠餐具和塑膠產品管制]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[走塑]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1231297</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>首階段「走塑」經已實施數日，坊間大量食肆已跟從政策改用替代環保餐具。今日有環保餐具供應商示範以竹刀叉鋸牛扒，示範期間竹叉兩度折斷。</p><blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C6K-zoOIUEt/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14"><div style="padding: 16px;"><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display: block; height: 50px; margin: 0 auto 12px; width: 50px;"></div><div style="padding-top: 8px;"><div style="color: #3897f0; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 550; line-height: 18px;">在 Instagram 查看這則貼文</div></div><div style="padding: 12.5% 0;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; margin-bottom: 14px; align-items: center;"><div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(0px) translateY(7px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; height: 12.5px; transform: rotate(-45deg) translateX(3px) translateY(1px); width: 12.5px; flex-grow: 0; margin-right: 14px; margin-left: 2px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(9px) translateY(-18px);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: 8px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 20px; width: 20px;"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: auto;"><div style="width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);"></div></div></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 224px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 144px;"></div></div><p style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; padding: 8px 0 7px; text-align: center; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;"><a style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C6K-zoOIUEt/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LIHKG 討論區（@lihkg.forum）分享的貼文</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//www.instagram.com/embed.js"></script></p><p>首階段即棄膠餐具和塑膠產品管制已於本月 22 日正式實施，有市民認為環保餐具耐用度低、容易斷裂，故環保署今日設立「綠色餐具平台」，為餐具供應商提供展示環保餐具的平台，但有供應商示範使用拼接竹刀叉鋸牛扒時竹叉兩次斷裂。</p><p>據港台引述其他環保餐具供應商指，市民需要時間適應環保餐具，另外又指示範餐具屬「拼接餐具」，能夠節省材料，以壓低成本，但餐具接駁口容易磨損斷裂。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1750505-20240425.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/john-lee-said-no-plastic-doesnot-affect-citizen/life-tech/green-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">李家超：「走塑」對市民影響不大，謝展寰：如替代餐具不耐用可試其他產品</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/22/paper-straw-pfas/life-tech/health/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">比利時大學：「走塑」紙飲管也可致癌 + 不育，研究指有不可降解 PFAS</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/25/bamboo-knife-cut-steak-broke-twice/life-tech/green-2/">【走塑】供應商示範竹刀叉鋸扒但兩度截斷，負責人：市民需時間適應</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
