            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>微信支付宣佈外國人可使用微信支付「數字人民幣」，毋須提供個人資料。</p><p>微信設有多種「小程式」，支援在酒旅、餐飲、零售使用「數字人民幣」，據《cnBeta》報道，中國人民銀行先前發布的《境外來華人士數字人民幣支付指南》，表示外籍人士去中國旅遊後可註冊帳號，按照説明開設「數字人民幣」錢包，隨即可以用「數字人民幣」App 掃微信支付商業收款碼與經營收款碼支付。</p><p>《境外來華人士數字人民幣支付指南》指，外籍人士可使用國際銀行卡付款，如使用「數字人民幣」匿名錢包，不需提供護照，亦無須親自前往銀行辦理境內帳户。現時微信支付「數字人民幣」可以使用逾 210 個國家手機號碼註冊。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231246" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150458-437x580.jpg" alt="" width="437" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150458-437x580.jpg 437w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150458.jpg 679w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 437px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231247" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150508-369x580.jpg" alt="" width="369" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150508-369x580.jpg 369w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150508.jpg 572w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 369px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231248" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150516-557x580.jpg" alt="" width="557" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150516-557x580.jpg 557w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150516.jpg 746w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 557px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231249" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150551-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150551-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240425150551.jp